I want to build a home
===================

	Ø Land
	Ø Plan or blue print --> rooms, floors, kitchen, floor tiles, windows, lift, steps
	Ø Materials
	Ø Engineers
	Ø Measuring tools
	Ø Builders
	Ø House 


If we don’t have a proper plan or blue print wt will happen?
=================================================

	Ø We can't build a house within the given timeline
	Ø Need more materials
	Ø Need more expenses 
	Ø You have to more money for extra days to the builders
	Ø There is no proper direction

If you set up any infrastructure manually wt will happen?
==============================================

	Ø It will take more time
	Ø Manual errors
	Ø It is difficult to manage infrastructure 
	Ø It is difficult to automate infrastructure 
	Ø It is difficult to track and versioning ur infrastructure 

Solution by terraform
==================
	Ø It will save time
	Ø It will reduce manual errors
	Ø It is easy to manage infrastructure 
	Ø It is easy to automate infrastructure 
	Ø It is easy track and versioning ur infrastructure 
	Ø To reusable infrastructure 

I want to deploy a application wt do I need?
====================================

	Ø Servers
	Ø Networks
	Ø Database
	Ø Storages


Terraform prerequisites
====================

	Ø  code or script   --> blue-print
	Ø Terraform cli + aws cli + access keys + providers  --> builders
	Ø Infrastructure   --> house 

	Ø Terraform always requires one working directory or a folder

Us-east-1:-  us-east-1a, us-east-1b,  us-east-1c, us-east-1d,

Ap-south-1:-  ap-osuth-1a,  ap-south-1b


